</a>



<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="99">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$xiao-yao-jian-xian-67" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/xiao-yao-jian-xian-67" class="zg-link" title="逍遥剑仙">逍遥剑仙</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$jin-zhen-gu-mei-zhi" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/jin-zhen-gu-mei-zhi" class="zg-link" title="李佳琪">李佳琪</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$lei-ling-95" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/lei-ling-95" class="zg-link" title="雷零">雷零</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="736550" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">谢♂邀。<br><br>首先看不按肯定是不行：<br><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/e6756f2a8c63063ce76731b7bc6808f8_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="205" data-rawheight="246" class="content_image" width="205"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="205" data-rawheight="246" class="content_image lazy" width="205" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/e6756f2a8c63063ce76731b7bc6808f8_b.jpg"><br><br>一种比较好的方法是直接席地而坐：<br><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/49ca28f6525ea687f3025352c7d54ff0_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="550" data-rawheight="413" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="550" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/49ca28f6525ea687f3025352c7d54ff0_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="550" data-rawheight="413" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="550" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/49ca28f6525ea687f3025352c7d54ff0_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/49ca28f6525ea687f3025352c7d54ff0_b.jpg"><br>但是会弄脏裙子。我们可以从空气动力学上考虑，加一块安定面来改变整个下半身的压力场：<br><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/2680b1bde3598098efd7d5f573632411_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="283" data-rawheight="329" class="content_image" width="283">你看那个蓝色的纱巾是关键，这么跑都没有让风把裙子吹起来。</noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="283" data-rawheight="329" class="content_image lazy" width="283" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/2680b1bde3598098efd7d5f573632411_b.jpg">你看那个蓝色的纱巾是关键，这么跑都没有让风把裙子吹起来。<br><br>但是纱巾不太好搭配，这时候可以考虑把手包的位置放低：<br><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/6dbeaf8e72575f599a1edb98305c9c1a_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="334" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/6dbeaf8e72575f599a1edb98305c9c1a_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="334" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="500" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/6dbeaf8e72575f599a1edb98305c9c1a_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/6dbeaf8e72575f599a1edb98305c9c1a_b.jpg"><br>你看刚一把包放下立马就给吹起来：<br><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/7ba4383314578dc4b761bf38c2a1fe64_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="253" data-rawheight="199" class="content_image" width="253"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="253" data-rawheight="199" class="content_image lazy" width="253" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/7ba4383314578dc4b761bf38c2a1fe64_b.jpg"><br>根据风向及时调整可以达到最佳效果：<br><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/1ab96fb215c91d75334ecf9b0116cb2c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="431" data-rawheight="576" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="431" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/1ab96fb215c91d75334ecf9b0116cb2c_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="431" data-rawheight="576" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="431" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/1ab96fb215c91d75334ecf9b0116cb2c_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/1ab96fb215c91d75334ecf9b0116cb2c_b.jpg"><br>要是连包都没有怎么办？你看要起风先给他一把扯住！<br><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/29fa291f800d6d8b7c469b904d36071e_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="450" data-rawheight="337" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="450" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/29fa291f800d6d8b7c469b904d36071e_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="450" data-rawheight="337" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="450" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/29fa291f800d6d8b7c469b904d36071e_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/29fa291f800d6d8b7c469b904d36071e_b.jpg"><br>最后还是没扯住咋整？在风来的一瞬间你就得跟项少龙这么按才能最大程度避免走光：<br><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/20c01c8cdecb7aceca2f1d89610f11db_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="496" class="content_image" width="400"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="496" class="content_image lazy" width="400" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/20c01c8cdecb7aceca2f1d89610f11db_b.jpg"><br>别说风了，甄嬛都掀不起来。


</div>

